<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Overview</h3>
    <p class="text-block_role">Role: Discovery, UX, UI Design</p>
    <p class="text-block_copy">Infor Ming.le Streams is an important core product for Infor that enables you to organize recurring processes with the ability to involve internal and external participants. As a designer on the Ming.le pod, my job was to design the native tablet experience for Streams for both iOS and Android. The tablet experience allows participants to organize processes on the go. Stream participants can collaborate seamlessly to complete activities, create new streams from templates, organize documents by threading them around each activity and quickly view the status of all tasks.</p>
</section>

