<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Challenge</h3>
    <p class="text-block_copy">The biggest challenge for designing the tablet version of Streams was not having a good user experience foundation to build from the desktop application. It was a bit outdated in its design and lacking in overall usability. The main points of frustration for our users was not being able to see all streams at once and quickly get the status of each stream. It was also difficult to sort through current streams based on the filter views being obscure icons.</p>

    <p class="text-block_copy">From our initial research with current Streams users, we knew we needed to simplify the streams creation process for the tablet experience and this meant cutting features while making sure users could still complete all core Streams tasks on the go.</p>
</section>

