<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Solution</h3>
    <p class="text-block_copy">The end result was a native tablet experience that streamlined the following processes: allowing the user to see an overview of all active streams, create a new stream from a premade templates, and limited customization options for editing the steps in each stream. I sketched the initial screens to define these user flows. Later, I created prototypes of these user flows to use for user testing and eventually the handoff to our developer team. I was able to quickly iterate the design of both Android and iOS versions of this application based on user feedback.</p>
</section>

